summary: Changes the outfit of the dibellapriestress
descriptionHtml:
A long time ago(ten minutes) I thought about the fact that these priestress of beauty hind there beauty.So I decided to give them the Tavernwench outfit.

UPDATE Ver.1.1:
Hamal now wears the Nocturnal robe
Anwen now wears DreamBurrows Sage Outfit retexture
Now requires DreamBurrows Sage Outfit Retexture Standalone by DreamBurrow 

Required:
DreamBurrows Sage Outfit Retexture Standalone by DreamBurrow  http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=17699

Future:I will change the outfits of the rest later,at the moment its enough xD
Add new Screenshots (tomorrow)

Known bugs:
3 of them have a strange skin tone with the outfit.

Credits:
Thx Backsteppo for your Dragon Quest 3 Sage Outfit for UNP mod
Thx DreamBurrow for your retexture 

Link to the original outfit of Backsteppo: skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=9387
